{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/dev/knowledge/functional","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"fd5708d3-b96f-5ba4-8556-a08ca4bb0789","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"선언형-개발방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8%ED%98%95-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"선언형 개발방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>선언형 개발방식,</h2>\n<h1 id=\"함수형-프로그래밍-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%ED%98%95-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D-\" aria-label=\"함수형 프로그래밍  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>함수형 프로그래밍 !</h1>\n<p><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"함수형-프로그래밍이란-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%ED%98%95-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80-\" aria-label=\"함수형 프로그래밍이란  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>함수형 프로그래밍이란 ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">다양한 함수를 조합해서 소프트웨어를 만드는 방식이에요.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">알고리즘이 아닌, 목표만을 명시한다는 특징이 있어요.\n\n  명령형은 어떻게 (How) 라면,\n  선언형은 무엇을 (What) 에 집중!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">단순히 함수를 사용한다가 아니라,\n\n함수를 값으로써 보고 프로그래밍 하는거죠!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">예를 들자면, JavaScript 의 콜백?</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"왜-함수형-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%99%9C-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%ED%98%95-\" aria-label=\"왜 함수형  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>왜 함수형 ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">부수효과 없이,\n\n안정적이고 예측 가능한 프로그램을 구성할 수 있기 때문이죠!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"어떻게-동작하길래-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%96%B4%EB%96%BB%EA%B2%8C-%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B8%EB%9E%98-\" aria-label=\"어떻게 동작하길래  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>어떻게 동작하길래 ?</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">외부변수에 대해서는 정보의 절대값이 아닌,\n\n주소값을 기준으로 동작해요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"순수함수-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%88%9C%EC%88%98%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-\" aria-label=\"순수함수  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>순수함수 ?</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">같은 입력에 대해서는 항상 같은 출력을 내는 함수에요!\n\n외부 변수에 대한 영향을 받지 않아요!\n\n함수를 값으로써 바라볼 수 있는 이유죠!\n\n멀티 스레드 작업에서 안전하고, 병렬적인 계산이 가능해요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"익명함수-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B5%EB%AA%85%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-\" aria-label=\"익명함수  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>익명함수 ?</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">이름이 없이, 실행내용만을 가진 함수에요!\n\n예를 들자면,\n\nPython 의 Lambda, JavaScript 의 Arrow Function 이 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"고계함수\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%A0%EA%B3%84%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98\" aria-label=\"고계함수 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>고계함수?</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">함수를 다루는 함수.\n\n즉, 함수를 인자로 받아서, 결과값을 내는 함수에요!\n\n다른 함수를 반환하는 함수도 고계함수라고 해요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"구성과-설계-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EA%B3%BC-%EC%84%A4%EA%B3%84-\" aria-label=\"구성과 설계  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구성과 설계 !</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">입력과 출력을 중심으로 함수를 구성하고,\n\n각각의 함수는 자신의 역할만 하도록 설계해요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"응용방법-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%91%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95-\" aria-label=\"응용방법  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>응용방법 !</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">다양한 순수함수, 익명함수, 고계함수를 조합해서,\n\n프로그램이 동작하는 중에 임의의 함수가 생성되도록 설계할 수도 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">여러 인자를 받는 함수에 일부 인자만 넣어서,\n\n나머지 인자를 받는 다른 함수를 만들어내는,\n\n&#39;커링&#39; 방식을 이용할 수도 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">컬렉션 내의 요소들을 다양하게, 연속적으로 처리할 수 있는\n\n함수 조합기 (function combinator) 도 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">예를 들자면,\n\n    Python 과 JavaScript 의 map(),\n\n    JavaScript 의 forEach() ?</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/dev/knowledge/functional","tagSlugs":["/tag/knowledge/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-29","description":"함수형 프로그래밍에 대한 글입니다.","tags":["knowledge"],"title":"함수형 프로그래밍 ?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/dev/knowledge/functional"}}}